{"tid":1106352,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲前要做嘅事(2)- 「出走一趟烏克蘭。」","createTime":"2019-04-14T13:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:41:43.000Z","uid":188643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30ff9a369a42e8aad0d4301c13ac99feaf709172","tid":1106352,"uid":188643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的。有日朋友問東歐旅遊啲料，左執右執發覺其實都有好多嘢可以分享，再加上見到隔離post再提烏克蘭，心血來潮想講多啲呢段出走旅程嘅見聞感受。但唔知用咩形式好，出住一個一齊慢慢傾。<br />\n<br />\n城市：Rivne (聽講意指一條直路）<br />\n話說有次夜晚先到達城市Rivne，幾經波折先終於搵到間Hostel入住，當晚同一個嚟至首都嘅爸爸傾咗好多話題。據知佢做生意要遊走城市間第二朝已經唔見咗人，我亦不以為然繼續旅程。<br />\n直到我要再次換錢，伸手入牛仔褲前面啲褲袋，竟然跌咗張寫滿字嘅 1hrn，一睇就係爸爸送畀我呢位投緣陌生人嘅小小心意，當堂好窩心同埋好驚，諗點解咁好人同埋點解我啲衫褲放得咁貼身整齊佢都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnFf1SL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnFf1SL.png&h=b3d14dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHXexZv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHXexZv.png&h=29f57e29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/213112_5c70a2df6ed9afe97b10732398c48b45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F213112_5c70a2df6ed9afe97b10732398c48b45.png&h=d07ab8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/213152_555fcc4b537a4aa12548b93e3302e84e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F213152_555fcc4b537a4aa12548b93e3302e84e.png&h=c1d0a6d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a643fe12ad7b31360ec87c778d7fc51f9a2180c4","tid":1106352,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名"},{"pid":"e70d48a5e7d3e6c69ae0